### Add Sweet (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/sweets
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Chocolate Truffle",
  "category": "Chocolate",
  "price": 50,
  "quantity": 100,
  "description": "Rich dark chocolate truffles",
  "image": "http://example.com/truffle.jpg"
}

### Add Another Sweet (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/sweets
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rasgulla",
  "category": "Bengali",
  "price": 20,
  "quantity": 200
}

### List All Sweets
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sweets

### Search Sweets by Name
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sweets?search=Chocolate

### Filter Sweets by Category
GET http://localhost:5000/api/sweets?category=Bengali

